This folder contains all the source codes from P-BBNIP2. To replicate the experiments, edit the 
"main_Problem2_Pes.py" file to change the input instance file names (make sure to add the complete
path to the network file or to add the network file to the same folder). Also, make sure to scroll
down the "main_Problem2.Pes" file to edit/update the names of the result files according to your experiments.
